Bitcoin implemented in perl, meant to be portable.

Status:
 Work in progress.

Usage:
 perl bitcoin.pl

For speed it's recommended to place db file on memory filesystem like this:
 mount -t tmpfs -o size=10g tmpfs `pwd`/var
 mount -o remount,size=15G tmpfs /.1/

Features:
- web interface
- data stored in SQL database via DBI (SQLite by default)
- blockchain download
- chain branches
- key management with confirmed amount and unconfirmed delta

"Do what you want" license.

links:
 https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Protocol_specification
 https://github.com/bitcoin/bips
 https://bitcoin.org/en/developer-examples#p2sh-multisig

